kill the nine justices of the U.S. Supreme Court.
   George Thomas Haley, 38, was arrested without incident Friday
afternoon in the Washington suburb of Arlington, Va., said Bill
Dempsey, spokesman at the Alexandria, Va., field office of the U.S.
