   One day short of her 85th birthday, Mrs. Dukakis was living the
ultimate American dream, visiting the island where she landed more
than 75 years ago as a 9-year-old Greek immigrant, with a son who
was the Democratic candidate for president of her adopted land.
   Panos Dukakis, who would later meet and marry Euterpe, passed
through Ellis Island a year before her.
   ``Their story is your story, it is our story, it is the story of
