<HEAD>Belgian August Jobless Rate Down From A Year Ago</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BRUSSELS, Belgium (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Belgium's unemployment rate fell to
11.4 percent in August from a year ago but was up slightly from
July, the government reported Friday.
   Last month's rate compares with a 12.3 percent level in August
1987 and an 11.3 percent rate in July.
