Exchange.
   October live cattle fell to 72.00 cents a pound from 72.97
cents; September feeder cattle moved to 81.35 cents a pound from
82.25 cents; October hogs slipped to 38.52 cents a pound from 41.05
cents; and February frozen pork bellies dropped to 48.65 cents a
pound from 54.82 cents.
