September silver dipped to $6.518 a troy ounce from $6.660.
   Energy futures retreated on the New York Mercantile Exchange.
   October West Texas Intermediate crude oil dropped to $14.79 a
barrel from $15.34; September heating oil slipped to 42.88 cents a
gallon from 43.35 cents; and September unleaded gasoline fell to
43.98 cents a gallon from 44.57.
